        <abstract> 
<p>Is glad Fd’AF will find Wallace’s work useful [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">13313</hi>].</p>  
<p>Has examined the egg-cases of <hi rend="italic">Blatta</hi> and suspects the white matter may be cement or plaster. If Fd’AF observes similar cases the fact would be worth publishing as a good instance of skill in protection.</p> 
        </abstract>
